To reset the game run either reset.bat or reset.sh depending on your
system.

To run the door, execute the following command

           portvic.exe -D [DROPFILE]

where [DROPFILE] is the full path and filename of the dropfile. Ensure
that the working directory is the Port Victoria directory. Use door32.sys
on Windows, and door.sys on Linux.

For a full list of available options, type

           portvic.exe -?
